{"title":"咱坐在驾驶台上","authors":["谢其规"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱坐在驾驶台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢其规"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雨，你下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风，你刮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们试车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是按照原计划。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿起雨衣，上车！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风雨出厂门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高歌进发！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱的压路机，啥也不怕："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上坡，脚跟稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下桥，身不斜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车灯一亮前程明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前压！向前压！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这深夜的黄浦江边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱坐在驾驶台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听得见纽约街头的失业工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜷缩着饿瘪的身躯在呻吟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看得见日本三池煤矿里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工头的皮鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把矿工抽昏在地下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱也听得见南越人民武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇袭美国侵略者的炮声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱也看得见呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在刚果河畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已站起千万个卢蒙巴……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时呵这时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱感到火热的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放在咱肩上的担子多重大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时呵这时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压路机拉开嗓门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界说话——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风风雨雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国无产阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远把红旗在革命的驾驶台上高插！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}